<string name="watch_tether_info_title">⌚ Watch Tether — How It Works</string>
<string name="watch_tether_info_body">When enabled, Thieves Trap monitors the Bluetooth connection to your paired smartwatch in the background.\n\n🔒 If the watch disconnects:\n   • Screen locks immediately via Device Admin\n   • Repeating vibration alert fires\n   • A 5-minute silent countdown begins\n\n✅ During the countdown you can tap:\n   • \"I\'m Safe\" — cancels, no PIN required\n   • \"🚨 TRIGGER ALARM\" — max-volume siren\n   • \"🔕 DISARM / MUTE\" — stops alarm + cancels\n\n📩 If the countdown expires, one emergency SMS with GPS is sent to your Emergency Contact.</string>
<string name="watch_tether_info_button">Got It</string>
<string name="plan_b_info_title">🔐 Secure Plan B Commands</string>
<string name="plan_b_info_body">By default, commands without a PIN send alerts only to your registered emergency contacts.\n\nHowever, if you append your live APP PIN (e.g., \"WHERE 2026\"), the app will bypass all registration limits and reply directly to that unknown sender\'s phone!\n\nThis PIN updates dynamically in real-time whenever you modify it inside the application settings.</string>
<string name="plan_b_info_button">Got it</string>
